cli_content:
Flags:  D - down        P - bundled in port-channel
        I - stand-alone s - suspended
        d - down        S - default port

Group  Port-channel  Protocol    Ports
------+-------------+-----------+-------------------------------------------------
1      Po1          LACP         Gi0/1(P)  Gi0/2(P)
2      Po2          LACP         Gi0/3(D)  Gi0/4(d)  Gi0/5(P)
3      Po3          LACP         Gi0/6(s)  Gi0/7(S)
textfsm_template:
Value GROUP (\d+)
Value PORT_CHANNEL (Po\d+)
Value PROTOCOL (\S+)
Value PORTS (.+)

Start
  ^Group\s+Port-channel\s+Protocol\s+Ports\s*$$
  ^-+\s+-+\s+-+\s+-+\s*$$
  ^\s*${GROUP}\s+${PORT_CHANNEL}\s+${PROTOCOL}\s+${PORTS}\s*$$ -> Record
